AUDIENCE: Since PPA is only
valued for one year, so how do

00:43:24.180 --> 00:43:27.160
you make the decision to go for
the full patent or just

00:43:27.160 --> 00:43:28.040
leave the idea?

00:43:28.040 --> 00:43:29.580
STEPHEN KEY: That's
a great question.

